## Activation Protocol

<!-- WHY: D1 (Activation Protocol) — this section is MANDATORY. It defines what Claude Code loads -->
<!-- WHY: before producing any output. Without this, the knowledge base is unused. -->
<!-- WHY: Order matters: load general context first, specific context second. -->
